<s> Hugh  </s>
<s> This is not a Dia Bug.  </s>
<s> Dia's export filter seems to work pretty well, based on the august SVG specification, before that SVG 1.0 was released as a recommandation.  </s>
<s> That's why Doctype declaration differs.  </s>
<s> Amaya recognizes Dia's SVG, but the current implementation of SVG in Amaya is not yet complete.  </s>
<s> The Dialog named "Parsing error", that can be accessed from the view menu, diplays warnings for unsupported SVG tags in Amaya.  </s>
<s> There isn't any SVG validator for now.  </s>
